		<div class="comment-body"><p>&#8220;Forskjeller betyr ingenting for annet enn misunnelsen&#8221;</p>
<p>Her er noen eksempler på hva økonomiske forskjeller gjør med folk:</p>
<p>&#8220;Research has shown an inverse link between income inequality and social cohesion. In more equal societies, people are much more likely to trust each other, measures of social capital suggest greater community involvement, and homicide rates are consistently lower.&#8221;</p>
<p><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economic_inequality#Social_cohesion" rel="nofollow">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economic_inequality#Social_cohesion</a></p>
<p>&#8220;Recently, there has been increasing interest from epidemiologists on the subject of economic inequality and its relation to the health of populations. There is a very robust correlation between socioeconomic status and health. &#8221;</p>
<p><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economic_inequality#Population_health" rel="nofollow">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economic_inequality#Population_health</a></p>
